      • addAllOnEnd

        public void addAllOnEnd(javafx.scene.Node... nodes)
        Add multiple nodes to the toolbar. Those nodes are added by id and will appear on the end of the toolbar Means right hand side for ToolbarPosition.NORTH and ToolbarPosition.SOUTH and on the bottom for ToolbarPosition.EAST and ToolbarPosition.WEST The id is the name of the calling component by default. For self-managed ids see addAllOnEnd(String id, Node... nodes)
        Parameters:
        nodes - the nodes to add
